episodes.title: Death To... Drag Queens, Cults & Birthday Cake feat. Eve Elle
episodes.description: This week the celestial goddesses are joined by Adelaide's finest, Eve Elle! The gals discuss what should be spared from the impending apocalypse. Which Australian drag queen, which cult and what type of birthday treat will people be served.   Find out now! Follow Eve here: IG: @misseveelle  Death To Everyone!!!
